{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Martin Bokša Blog","author":"Martin Bokša","gitUrl":"https://github.com/martinboksa/portfolio/"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9d8df735-5f25-5890-8361-c36d827cb7b3","excerpt":"Za posledný môj rok som sa stretol s množstvom knižníc, ktoré sa týkajú Reactu.\nJe to dané najmä tým, že som nemal veľké predchádzajúce skúsenosti s Reactom\na…","html":"<p>Za posledný môj rok som sa stretol s množstvom knižníc, ktoré sa týkajú Reactu.\nJe to dané najmä tým, že som nemal veľké predchádzajúce skúsenosti s Reactom\na zároveň javascript je tak rýchly jazyk, že vychádzá v ňom každý deň\nnové množstvo knižníc.\nRád by som si tu odložil doterajšie skúsenosti a priblížil vám čo všetko považujem\ndnes za nevynutné vedieť pri práci s Reactom. Knižnice môžu pomôcť hlavne tým, ktorí\ns ním začínajú.</p>\n<h2 id=\"boilerplate-kostra\"><a href=\"#boilerplate-kostra\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Boilerplate (Kostra)</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app\">create-react-app</a>\nak nemáte skúsenosti s Reactom, táto knižnica vám vytvorí boilerplate (alebo kostru) pre vašu\naplikáciu. Obsahuje všetky nevyhnuté konfigurácie a závislosti aby ste mohli\nrovno písať React a nemuseli sa o nič starať.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"no-text\"><pre class=\"language-no-text\"><code class=\"language-no-text\">What&#39;s included? React, JSX, ES6, TypeScript and Flow syntax support.</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"data-store\"><a href=\"#data-store\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Data Store</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/reduxjs/react-redux\">Redux</a> ide o globálny obchod s premennými. Je vhodný k tomu,\naby ste nemuseli preposielať premennú cez ďalších <em>x</em> komponent do hĺbky. Tak ju\nnapojíte na globálne obchod. Použitie napríklad: user data, aktuálna téma, stav aplikácie, …\nPoužíva sa často. Odporúčam si doinštalovať na vývijanie <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/redux-devtools/lmhkpmbekcpmknklioeibfkpmmfibljd?hl=en\">plugin</a> do chrome.\nAk sa chcete vyhnúť boilerplate, ktorý je spojený s Reduxom, odporúčam <a href=\"https://github.com/rematch/rematch\">rematch</a>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.24091778202677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Redux\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/1a291/redux.png 148w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/2bc4a/redux.png 295w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png 590w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/526de/redux.png 885w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fa2eb/redux.png 1180w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png 1569w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/context.html\">React Context</a> je to pomerne nová feature od Reactu.\nJe teoretickým nahraditeľom Reduxu. Tu sa, ale vytvorí <code class=\"language-text\">provider</code> dát a\njeho vnútorné komponenty vo vnútri ich vedia čitať pomocou <code class=\"language-text\">consumera</code>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 321px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.40498442367601%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"React Context\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/09b75/react-context.png 148w,\n/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/438fb/react-context.png 295w,\n/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png 321w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mobxjs/mobx\">MobX</a> ďalšia možnosť k uskladneniu\nglobálnych dát.</p>\n<h2 id=\"serverová-komunikácia\"><a href=\"#serverov%C3%A1-komunik%C3%A1cia\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Serverová komunikácia</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\">fetch</a> natívny príkaz z ES6,\nktorým je možné dopytovať server. Funguje pomocou <strong>Promise</strong>, ale chýbajú mu zatiaľ\nnejaké funkcie ako napríklad <strong>abort</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/axios/axios\">Axios</a> rozšírená verzia <strong>fetch</strong>, založená\nna XMLHttpRequests.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber 0\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> axios <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'axios'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\naxios\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/user?ID=12345'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>response<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>response<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/ky\">Ky</a> kolega poradil prácu s touto knižnicou, ktorý je založený na fetch. Porovnanie autora.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Quote here.</p>\n<p>— <cite>Benjamin Franklin</cite></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client\">Apollo Client</a> knižnica s plnou podporou\npre <a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>. Ponúka tiež <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/apollo-client-developer-t/jdkknkkbebbapilgoeccciglkfbmbnfm\">dev tools</a> pre Chrome.\nOdporúčam si to pozrieť. <strong>GraphQL</strong> v skratke: Viacero dopytov je možné zlúčiť do jedného.\nAlebo namiesto reťazových volaní na server, je možné ich nahradiť za jeden.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/c0967/graphql.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.59539918809201%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"GraphQL\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/fb8a0/graphql.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/1a291/graphql.png 148w,\n/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/2bc4a/graphql.png 295w,\n/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/fb8a0/graphql.png 590w,\n/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/526de/graphql.png 885w,\n/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/fa2eb/graphql.png 1180w,\n/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/c0967/graphql.png 1478w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2 id=\"css\"><a href=\"#css\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/styled-components/styled-components\">Styled Component</a> vizualizácia\nkomponentov v javascripte pomocou CSS. Výhodou je napríklad vynutie sa class-name konfliktov.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber 0\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n  display: inline-block;\n  color: #e62076;\n`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Button href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.martinboksa.eu/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>GitHub<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Button<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui\">Material UI</a> React\nkomponenty, ktoré implementujú <a href=\"https://material-ui.com/\">Google Material dizajn</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/JedWatson/classnames\">classnames</a> zaradil som to do CSS, ale ide skôr\no utilitu, ktorá pomáha vytvárať class-names pre komponenty. Je to jeden z mojích\nnajobľúbenejších nástrojov. Podľa mňa výborne zprehľadní kód.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">classNames</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// => result class name: 'foo bar'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/contra/react-responsive\">react-responsive</a> jednoduchý spôsob ako použiť\nmedia query v Reacte.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber 0\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> MediaQuery <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-responsive'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Example</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Device Test<span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>MediaQuery query<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"(min-device-width: 1824px)\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>You have a huge screen<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>MediaQuery<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>MediaQuery query<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"(max-width: 1224px)\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>You are sized like a tablet or mobile phone though<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>MediaQuery<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/react-dnd/react-dnd\">React DnD</a> knižnica k vytvoreniu\nDrag&#x26;Drop rozhrania.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/react-spring/react-spring\">React Spring</a> knižnica na animácie. Mám veľmi dobrú skúsenosť s výkonom\naký je možný s ňou dosiahnúť. Odporúčam\nsi pozrieť <a href=\"https://blog.usejournal.com/why-react-needed-yet-another-animation-library-introducing-react-spring-8212e424c5ce\"><em>“Prečo React potrebuje ďalšiu knižnicu na animácie?”</em></a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/dragndrop-c409f1a43fcb00ed186997b56efe72ab.gif\" alt=\"React Spring - Drag&#x26;Drop\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/react-bootstrap/react-bootstrap\">React Bootstrap</a> komponenty\nna základe <a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/\">Bootstrap 4</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"internationalization\"><a href=\"#internationalization\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Internationalization</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/yahoo/react-intl\">React Intl</a> knižnica na preklady, ktorá okrem iného poskytuje\nformátovanie dátumov, čísiel, reťazcov, pluralizácie, …</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/i18next/react-i18next\">react-i18next</a> internacionalizácie pre <em>reactjs</em> / <em>reactnative</em>, ktorý je založený na i18next.</p>\n<p>V tejto časti by som sám rad zistil aké sú ďalšie spoľahlivé možnosti._</p>\n<h2 id=\"testing\"><a href=\"#testing\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Testing</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://jestjs.io/en/\">Jest</a> testovacia platforma s nulovou konfiguráciou. Používa ho tiež <em>Facebook</em>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/airbnb/enzyme\">Enzyme</a> testovací nástroj od <em>Airbnb</em>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"meta-tags\"><a href=\"#meta-tags\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Meta Tags</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/gaearon/react-document-title\">React Document Title</a> nastavenie <code class=\"language-javascript\">title</code> pomocout <code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>DocumentTitle</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Awesome Title<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/nfl/react-helmet\">React Helmet</a> nástroj na správu hlavičiek <code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"formuláre\"><a href=\"#formul%C3%A1re\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Formuláre</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/erikras/redux-form\">Redux Form</a> Higher Order Component, ktorá drží\nstate v <em>reduxe</em>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"utils\"><a href=\"#utils\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Utils</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://lodash.com/docs/4.17.11\">lodash</a> rozširuje javascript o veľa zaujímavých funkciíí ako <em>debounce</em>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://momentjs.com/\">Moment.js</a> parsovanie, manipulácia a zobrazovanie dátumu a času 📅.</p>\n<h2 id=\"rich-editor\"><a href=\"#rich-editor\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Rich Editor</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/draft-js\">Draft.js</a> framework s ktorým je možné\nvytvoriť <em>rich editor</em>. \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 563px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.14209591474245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Rich Editor\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1539cd7870523d529ad6c5901a8dad27/b0abc/rich-editor.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1539cd7870523d529ad6c5901a8dad27/d8532/rich-editor.png 148w,\n/static/1539cd7870523d529ad6c5901a8dad27/9bf66/rich-editor.png 295w,\n/static/1539cd7870523d529ad6c5901a8dad27/b0abc/rich-editor.png 563w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h2 id=\"type-checking\"><a href=\"#type-checking\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Type Checking</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/prop-types\">PropTypes</a> kontrola typu <em>props</em> v runtime.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://flow.org/en/docs/frameworks/react/\">flow</a> statický typechecker.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/\">TypeScript</a> jazyk, ktorý sa prekladá do javascriptu, ale je typový. Odporúčam.</p>\n<h2 id=\"nice-to-know\"><a href=\"#nice-to-know\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Nice to know</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/storybooks/storybook\">Storybook</a> developerské rozrahnie pre UI komponenty. Vidíte ako vyzerajú vaše komponenty (za dôsledok sú podľa mňa komponenty, ktoré sa dajú lepšie znova použiť a testovať).\n<img src=\"/storybook-intro-5eb59c13f71816a543bf88170df88c36.gif\" alt=\"Storybook intro\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://prettier.io/\">Prettier</a> jeden z mojích ďalších obľúbených nástrojov. Slúži ako formátovač kódu, snáď všetky známe editory ho integrujú. Stačí stlačiť klávesovú skratku a naformátuje dokument.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://eslint.org/\">ESLint</a> <em>The pluggable linting utility for JavaScript and JSX.</em> Vo všetkých mojích projektoch som ho používal. Niekedy je otravný :).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://palantir.github.io/tslint/\">TSLint</a> Ako ESLint ale pre TypeScript, na statickú analýzu kód.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.pixijs.com/\">PixiJS</a> posledný rok som pracoval na grafickom editore v ktorom bol použitý PixiJS. Môžem plne odporučiť pri práci s grafikov.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\">Gatsby</a> pomáha vytvárať jednoducho stránky bez <em>“headache”</em>. Je v ňom napísaný napríklad <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/getting-started.html\">React Docs</a> alebo tento blog.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Knižníč a utilít na prácu s Reactom a javascriptom je naozaj veľa. Myslím, že toto je len zlomok zoznamu čo by vám mohlo byť užitočné.\nĎalších veľa knižníc môžete pozrieť <a href=\"https://github.com/brillout/awesome-react-components\">tu</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Necessary React libraries and skills!","date":"January 06, 2019"},"timeToRead":6}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/necessary-react-libraries/","previous":null,"next":null}}